- **Token schema (linkage):** see `docs/tokens.md` (⚛︎ color, ⌬ spacing, ∿ motion).  
- **Security:** sign zips; store checksums; restrict write; audit logs 👁️.

⸻

## 🧰 𝑪𝒐𝒅𝒆 𝒐𝒇 𝑪𝒓𝒂𝒇𝒕 (𝔇𝔒𝔇)
**A piece is “Done” when:**  
- [ ] ✠ Meets brief & constraints  
- [ ] 𓁹 AA contrast (or documented exception)  
- [ ] ⌬ Componentized; tokens applied  
- [ ] 🔤 Fonts licensed & embedded correctly  
- [ ] 🧪 Proofed on targets (retina, print stock, dark mode)  
- [ ] 🔐 Hashed & packaged with changelog

⸻

## 🗺 𝑴𝒂𝒑𝒑𝒊𝒏𝒈 (𝔈𝔱𝔥𝔬𝔰 → 𝔒𝔭𝔰)
